788
0:47:14,965 --> 0:47:23,674
Maybe this is where he came to rest.


789
0:47:23,674 --> 0:47:27,1
That is where,
after the flood was over,


790
0:47:27,1 --> 0:47:30,414
the Babylonian Noah
