791
0:47:30,414 --> 0:47:33,5
Apparently it was a pleasant
place to be


792
0:47:33,5 --> 0:47:35,552
where he could exist
without much work


793
0:47:35,552 --> 0:47:39,957
and pass the time away
as he pleased.


794
0:47:39,957 --> 0:47:42,526
If he did end up in Dilmun,


