0:47:42,526 --> 0:47:44,561
then the modern island of Bahrain


796
0:47:44,561 --> 0:47:52,736
may have a remarkable secret.


797
0:47:52,736 --> 0:47:54,204
Its landscape is dotted


798
0:47:54,204 --> 0:47:57,74
with hundreds of thousands
of burial mounds.


799
0:47:57,74 --> 0:47:58,909
And only a handful of these tombs


800
0:47:58,909 --> 0:48:1,11
have been excavated.


801
0:48:1,11 --> 0:48:4,948
But many date back
to Sumerian times.


802
0:48:4,948 --> 0:48:7,251
They are the sort of place
a great king


803
0:48:7,251 --> 0:48:15,359
would be laid to rest in.


804
0:48:15,359 --> 0:48:17,527
In time the memory of a king


805
0:48:17,527 --> 0:48:19,129
who survived a flood


806
0:48:19,129 --> 0:48:23,33
could have been turned
into a great Sumerian legend.


807
0:48:23,33 --> 0:48:24,234
It would have been embellished


808
0:48:24,234 --> 0:48:32,576
with miraculous
and mythological elements.


809
0:48:32,576 --> 0:48:35,212
Eventually it would have been
written down,


810
0:48:35,212 --> 0:48:38,882
copied and recopied
by generations of scribes,


811
0:48:38,882 --> 0:48:47,824
giving rise to new versions.


812
0:48:47,824 --> 0:48:49,626
Two thousand years later,


813
0:48:49,626 --> 0:48:51,28
one of those versions,


